e_item_assets/steam/apps/1836160/extras/1cd5c68cec3e036c3298260fd1c156d7.avif?t=1753744277\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836160/extras_big/1cd5c68cec3e036c3298260fd1c156d7.avif?t=1753744277 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join our discord server (in the links section of the game's Steam store page).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* all screenshots are taken with in game cinematic mode.</p>",
